C51 COMPILER V9.60.0.0   SCALERCOMMONTYPECRX0PD                                            10/18/2025 16:53:20 PAGE 330 

              
                      // 2. [0x65E0] Set Packet Type [5:3] : b'011 = HARD_RESET
